Peanut-Containing Product Recall Widget
----------------------------------------
A widget is an application that displays the featured content
directly on your Web page. You can embed content in personalized home
pages, blogs, and other sites. Once you've added the widget, there's
no technical maintenance. FDA.gov will update the content automatically.

To add it to your site, click on "Share" at the Source URL. A new
screen will display the html code for the widget. Simply cut and
paste the html code into your Web page.

Place this Peanut-Containing Product Recall Widget on your Web site,
portal home page, or in your blog to allow you and your visitors to
search for peanut-containing product recalls.

The code to add the Peanut-Containing Product Recall widget to your
site is available at the Source URL shown just above.

